{"id":20126,"date":"2015-01-03T17:47:55","date_gmt":"2015-01-03T13:47:55","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=20126"},"modified":"2020-12-23T17:28:56","modified_gmt":"2020-12-23T13:28:56","slug":"dhikr-allah-boasts-angels","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/01\/03\/dhikr-allah-boasts-angels\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Dhikr: Allah boasts to angels of those who remember Him"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Mu\u2019awiyah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came out to a gathering of his companions and he said, \u201c<strong>Why are you sitting<\/strong>?\u201d They said, \u201cWe are sitting to remember Allah and to praise him for guiding us to Islam and blessing us with it.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Only for Allah are you sitting for this?<\/strong>\u201d They said, \u201cBy Allah, we are only sitting for this.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Verily, I did not ask you for an oath because I doubted you. Rather, Gabriel has told me that Allah Almighty is proud of you in front of the angels.<\/strong>&#8221;<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2701<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Muslim<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u0646 \u0645\u0639\u0627\u0648\u064a\u0629 \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u062e\u064e\u0631\u064e\u062c\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u062d\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0629\u064d \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0635\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0647\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0642\u0